    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>演示版尚未翻译成简体中文，很快就会完成。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">探索与冒险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/055bb24db2b428118ec840146eef20ff.poster.avif?t=1772131738\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/055bb24db2b428118ec840146eef20ff.webm?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/055bb24db2b428118ec840146eef20ff.mp4?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个密集的手工打造世界等待探索，配备强大而有趣的移动系统，让你能去到任何地方。攀登最高的山峰，勇闯最深的水域，滑翔至遥远的土地，并发掘众多隐藏的宝藏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">宽容的技能导向战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/8b6e07fb43773e13d56fca77cfcc1f9e.poster.avif?t=1772131738\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/8b6e07fb43773e13d56fca77cfcc1f9e.webm?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/8b6e07fb43773e13d56fca77cfcc1f9e.mp4?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实时技能导向的战斗系统，你可以一键切换不同战斗风格。近战、远程、法术、格挡、闪避，尽情享受！并在战斗中切换不同武器，保持动态多变。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">单人 &amp; 合作多人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/23de69e951f574530dc7caa6a2e52e60.poster.avif?t=1772131738\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/23de69e951f574530dc7caa6a2e52e60.webm?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/23de69e951f574530dc7caa6a2e52e60.mp4?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即进即退，支持3人在线联机，并计划添加2人本地沙发同屏合作模式。无麻烦、无问题。你在单人游戏中培养进步的角色，将是你在合作模式中继续使用并进一步成长的同一个角色。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">自定义角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/90ef5cfd8e017ffb442ee6c03e1e4226.poster.avif?t=1772131738\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/90ef5cfd8e017ffb442ee6c03e1e4226.webm?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/90ef5cfd8e017ffb442ee6c03e1e4226.mp4?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用简易的角色创建器，从多种幻想种族中打造你的独特角色，真正脱颖而出。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">持续成长</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/38eba2e176f4128413e77011e7d00cfb.poster.avif?t=1772131738\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/38eba2e176f4128413e77011e7d00cfb.webm?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/38eba2e176f4128413e77011e7d00cfb.mp4?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的进度将伴随你左右，从单人到合作再到多次通关。甚至城镇升级也会带入新游戏+。每次击败地图最终首领，即可解锁全新难度层级——更高层级中，敌人更强悍，奖励与经验值却更为丰厚！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">职业技能与角色扮演</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/691da003bf92410c57ca4dd4036e422f.poster.avif?t=1772131738\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/691da003bf92410c57ca4dd4036e422f.webm?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/691da003bf92410c57ca4dd4036e422f.mp4?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将会有采矿、钓鱼、捕捉动物等多种乐趣活动。而且在多人模式中，你不受主机位置限制，可以自由按照自己的方式游玩，即使在他们的游戏里。你可以成为团队的矿工，搜寻最佳矿石，并交易给朋友换取他们珍贵的黄金！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">城镇商人与升级</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/7c598fe303d666b43af3442084a190cd.poster.avif?t=1772131738\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/7c598fe303d666b43af3442084a190cd.webm?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/7c598fe303d666b43af3442084a190cd.mp4?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拯救城镇居民，并利用收集的资源帮助他们重建昔日荣耀。铁匠、盔甲匠、秘法师和厨师也可以升级，从而获得出售和制作更好装备的能力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/fc227bfddc02abce359c1928353f990d.poster.avif?t=1772131738\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/fc227bfddc02abce359c1928353f990d.webm?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/fc227bfddc02abce359c1928353f990d.mp4?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数百年前，一股原始魔法从大地深处涌现，为帝国提供力量，却将居民与世界扭曲进腐败的魔爪之中。森林化为漆黑，天空流淌阴影，河流化为毒水。但一种较不常见的辐射能量也随之诞生，隐藏在纯净的战士体内——光战士（Luminaries）。他们手持光芒，目标是夺回土地，将枯萎病驱逐回去。然而，光战士的天赋是一把双刃剑：不朽的力量诱惑着灵魂。每隔80年，光战士必须将光芒传给继任者，否则将面临永恒的腐朽。那些违抗者囤积光芒，膨胀成神一般的黑暗暴君——黯君（Ebonarchs）。作为一名新生的光战士，崛起并增强力量。粉碎黯君的深渊力量源泉，剥夺他们的不朽，然后将他们击倒。与你的同伴光战士们一同，用光芒驱退黑暗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/766b2338f0a2f5898f707f24fa00524a.poster.avif?t=1772131738\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/766b2338f0a2f5898f707f24fa00524a.webm?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1648360/extras/766b2338f0a2f5898f707f24fa00524a.mp4?t=1772131738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
